content: We're soarin', flyin'. There's not a star in heaven that we can't reach. If we're trying, so we're breaking free. You know the world can see us in a way that's different than who we are. Creating space between us, 'til we're separate hearts. But your faith it gives me strength, strength to believe.
author: Zac Efron, Drew Seeley, Vanessa Hudgens
